name: app.R
content:
## app.R ##
library(shiny)
library(shinydashboard)
library(ggplot2)
library(tidyverse)

icb <- read.csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Asthma-and-Lungs/lwalc25/refs/heads/main/Health%20information%20by%20ICB.csv")
annual_review <- read.csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Asthma-and-Lungs/lwalc25/refs/heads/main/Annual%20review%20by%20ICB.csv")
annual_review_detail <- read.csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Asthma-and-Lungs/lwalc25/refs/heads/main/Annual%20review%20detail%20by%20ICB.csv")



#####Header#####
header<- dashboardHeader(title="Life with a Lung Condition Survey 2025", titleWidth=450)

#####Sidebar#####
sidebar<-dashboardSidebar(
  sidebarMenu(
    menuItem("Health information format", tabName = "HealthInformation", icon = icon("dashboard")),
    menuItem("Annual Reviews", tabName = "AnnualReviews", icon = icon("dashboard"))
  )
)

#####Body#####

body<-  dashboardBody(
  tabItems(
    # First tab content
    tabItem(tabName = "HealthInformation",
            h2("Health information format: preference and access"),
            fluidRow(
              box(
              title="ICB", width=4,
              selectInput("icbs1", "Select ICB", icb$demographics_icb)),
              infoBoxOutput("responses1"
              )),
            
            fluidRow(
              box(width=8, plotOutput("plot1", height=400))
            )

    ),
    # Second tab content
    tabItem(tabName = "AnnualReviews",
            h2("Have you had an annual review with a healthcare professional in the last year?"),
            fluidRow(
              box(
                title="ICB", width=3,
                selectInput("icbs2", "Select ICB", icb$demographics_icb)),
              infoBoxOutput("responses2", width=3),
              infoBoxOutput("f2f", width=3),
              infoBoxOutput("phone", width=3),
              infoBoxOutput("videocall", width=3),
              infoBoxOutput("online", width=3),
              infoBoxOutput("no", width=3)),
            fluidRow(
              box(width=8, plotOutput("plot2", height=400))
            )
    )))

#####Dashboard#####

ui <- dashboardPage(
  header,
  sidebar,
  body)


server <- function(input, output) {
  rval_data_sel<-reactive({icb%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs1)})
  
  rval_data_sel_2<-reactive({annual_review_detail%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs2)})
  
  rval_count<-reactive({icb%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs1)%>%
      group_by(demographics_icb)%>%
      summarize(sum=sum(info_count))})
  
  rval_count2<-reactive({annual_review%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs2)%>%
      group_by(demographics_icb)%>%
      summarize(sum=sum(count_review))})
  
  rval_f2f<-reactive({annual_review%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs2)%>%
      filter(annual_review=="Yes – face to face")%>%
      group_by(demographics_icb)%>%
      summarize(sum=sum(count_review))})
  
  rval_phone<-reactive({annual_review%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs2)%>%
      filter(annual_review=="Yes – over the phone")%>%
      group_by(demographics_icb)%>%
      summarize(sum=sum(count_review))})
  
  
  rval_videocall<-reactive({annual_review%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs2)%>%
      filter(annual_review=="Yes – via a videocall")%>%
      group_by(demographics_icb)%>%
      summarize(sum=sum(count_review))})
  
  rval_online<-reactive({annual_review%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs2)%>%
      filter(annual_review=="Yes – via online survey or text")%>%
      group_by(demographics_icb)%>%
      summarize(sum=sum(count_review))})
  
  rval_no<-reactive({annual_review%>%
      filter(demographics_icb==input$icbs2)%>%
      filter(annual_review=="No")%>%
      group_by(demographics_icb)%>%
      summarize(sum=sum(count_review))})
  
  output$responses1<-renderInfoBox({infoBox(paste0("Valid responses received: ", input$icbs1), rval_count()$sum, icon=icon("list"), color="light-blue", fill=TRUE)})
  
  output$responses2<-renderInfoBox({infoBox(paste0("Valid responses received: ", input$icbs2), rval_count2()$sum, icon=icon("list"), color="light-blue", fill=TRUE)})
  
  output$f2f<-renderInfoBox({infoBox("Yes – face to face", rval_f2f()$sum, icon=icon("list"), color="light-blue", fill=TRUE)})
  
  output$phone<-renderInfoBox({infoBox("Yes - over the phone", rval_phone()$sum, icon=icon("list"), color="light-blue", fill=TRUE)})
  
  output$videocall<-renderInfoBox({infoBox("Yes - via a videocall", rval_videocall()$sum, icon=icon("list"), color="light-blue", fill=TRUE)})
  
  output$online<-renderInfoBox({infoBox("Yes – via online survey or text", rval_online()$sum, icon=icon("list"), color="light-blue", fill=TRUE)})
  
  output$no<-renderInfoBox({infoBox("No", rval_no()$sum, icon=icon("list"), color="light-blue", fill=FALSE)})
  
  output$plot1<-renderPlot({
    ggplot(rval_data_sel())+
      aes(x=factor(information_format, levels=c("Digital format", "Physical format", "No preference")), y=info_count, fill=factor(information_format_access, levels=c("Yes", "No", "Not given")))+
      geom_col(position="dodge")+
      labs(x="Preferred format", y="Number of responses", title="Life with a Lung Condition Survey 2025", subtitle="Respondents' preferred health information format", fill="Do you receive information \nin your preferred format?")+
      scale_fill_manual(values=c("Yes" = "#ff3eb5", "No"="#440099", "Not given"="#ffb500"))+
      theme_grey(base_size=15)
      
      
  })
  
  output$plot2<-renderPlot({
    ggplot(rval_data_sel_2())+
      aes(x=factor(actions, levels=c("None of the above", "FeNO test", "Inhaler technique checked", "Digital self-management plan reviewed", "Paper self-management plan reviewed", "Medication discussed", "Exacerbations discussed","Symptoms discussed")), y=count_review_detail)+
      geom_col(fill="#440099")+
      labs(x="", y="Number of responses", title="Life with a Lung Condition Survey 2025", subtitle="If yes, which of the following happen during your last annual review?")+
      theme_grey(base_size=15)+
      coord_flip()
    
    
  })
}

shinyApp(ui, server)
